column16: Alberto Rosario grounds into a force out, third baseman Hernan Perez to second baseman Yadiel Rivera.   Greg Garcia out at 2nd.
Greg Garcia singles on a ground ball to center fielder Keon Broxton.
Carson Kelly grounds out, shortstop Orlando Arcia to first baseman Chris Carter.   Kolten Wong scores.
Brayan Pena grounds out softly, second baseman Yadiel Rivera to first baseman Chris Carter.   Kolten Wong to 2nd.
Dexter Fowler grounds out, second baseman Scooter Gennett to first baseman Chris Carter.
Javier Baez grounds out softly, third baseman Jonathan Villar to first baseman Chris Carter.   Jorge Soler to 3rd.    David Ross to 2nd.
David Ross walks.   Jorge Soler to 2nd.
Jason Heyward flies out to left fielder Jake Elmore.
Jorge Soler singles on a ground ball to shortstop Orlando Arcia.
Miguel Montero flies out to right fielder Hernan Perez.
Jason Heyward flies out to center fielder Keon Broxton.
Brewers challenged (tag play), call on the field was upheld: Chris Coghlan out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Hernan Perez.   Ben Zobrist scores.
Addison Russell hit by pitch.    Ben Zobrist to 2nd.
